            "body": "I was skeptical about paying more for cycling socks but these changed my mind completely. The arch support is fantastic and they feel like a second skin. Six months in and they still look brand new after dozens of washes.",
            "author": "Thomas M.",
            "date": "4 days ago",
            "rating": 5
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "review",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Great sock height",
            "body": "The tall sock look is exactly what I wanted. Sits perfectly at mid-calf and the elastic keeps them there. Clean look with any kit.",
            "author": "Lisa P.",
            "date": "1 week ago",
            "rating": 4
